; Coverage test for token.cc L210
; Date specifier that does not refer to a starting date.
; The word "monthly" is a period specifier without a concrete start date.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --display 'date < [monthly]' -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing value expression:
  date < [monthly]
         ^^^^^^^^^
Error: Date specifier does not refer to a starting date
end test
